		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Ah... the full quote.<br /><em>&quot;The Reset button on the Control Deck resets the PPU only on the front-loading NES (NES-001). On top-loaders (Famicom, NES-101), the Reset button resets only the CPU&quot;.</em><br /><br />Interesting. Just tested it in my emulator and - indeed - it scrambles the image and got opcode $12 as invalid.

		

